Enro Holding Corp said it acquired EnroShirt Co and Foxcroft Ltd from Wilson Bros for 30 mln dlrs.     Enro Holding is owned 50 pct by investors and 50 pct bymanagement and others. The investor group bought 50 pct of thecommon equity and supplied five mln dlrs in mezzaninefinancing. Management bought the other 50 pct. CongressFinancial Group supplied 28 mln dlrs in senior financing andthe seller took back a note for 12.1 mln dlrs.    Enro Shirt has annual sales of about 42 mln dlrs andFoxcroft has sales of about 13 mln dlrs. Reuter&#3;